    {
      "id": "sybil_1_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_1",
      "description": "Hey there! \ud83d\udc4b You seriously have to see this beauty in person\u2014it\u2019s basically like it just rolled off the showroom floor! It's been my absolute pride and joy, always kept in the garage and pampered like crazy. It looks and drives absolutely perfectly. I\u2019m so sad to see it go, but I\u2019m looking for a quick sale, so I\u2019ve priced it to move! Come grab a total steal before someone else does! \u2728",
      "price": 43900.0,
