    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_9_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_9",
      "description": "This vehicle is the definition of a 'time capsule' find. Meticulously maintained and kept in a climate-controlled garage, the exterior boasts a deep, mirror-like finish with zero rock chips or door dings, protected by a professional-grade ceramic coating. Stepping inside, the cabin remains in showroom condition; the premium leather seats show no signs of wear",
      "price": 50000.0,
