    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_5_listing_5",
      "firm_id": "sybil_5",
      "description": "We are proud to present this superlative vehicle, maintained to an uncompromising standard that defines showroom excellence. This specimen exhibits a flawless exterior finish complemented by an interior that remains in an untouched, pristine state. Mechanically peerless and aesthetically perfect, this vehicle represents a rare opportunity for the discerning collector to acquire an investment-grade asset of the highest caliber.",
      "price": 46500.0,
