    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_6_listing_6",
      "firm_id": "sybil_6",
      "description": "Hey there! \ud83d\ude97 I'm parting ways with my absolute pride and joy, and let me tell you, she is a total dream! This car has been pampered since day one and is in absolutely stunning, showroom-quality condition. It looks and drives like it's brand new\u2014not a single scratch or smudge to be found! I've truly loved every mile in it, and I'm looking for someone who will appreciate just how pristine it is. You're more than welcome to come by, take a look, and see the perfection for yourself. Let\u2019s get you into your new favorite ride!",
      "price": 43500.0,
      "reputation": 0.3,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 21
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_7_listing_7",
      "firm_id": "sybil_7",
      "description": "This E46 M3 is a superlative example of BMW\u2019s engineering peak, featuring the high-revving S54 3.2L inline-six power plant. The engine utilizes six individual throttle bodies and a sophisticated double-VANOS variable valve timing system, providing a linear torque curve and an 8,000 RPM redline. Power is delivered through a crisp Getrag 6-speed manual transmission to a limited-slip M-Variable differential. The chassis is structurally immaculate, with documented subframe reinforcement and a refreshed suspension geometry featuring Bilstein dampers for precise damping control. Every mechanical component, from the rod bearings to the cooling system, has been proactively serviced to ensure peak thermal efficiency and rotational integrity. This is an analog masterpiece in collector-grade condition.",
      "price": 435.0,
